def: An East Indian carnivorous mammal (Prionodon gracilis),resembling the civets, but without scent pouches. It is handsomelyspotted.
A tableau in which persons take part; also, specif., such atableau as imitating a work of art.
A mass of substances worn off from solid bodies by attrition,and reduced to small portions; as, diluvial detritus.
One who esteems; one who sets a high value on any thing.The proudest esteemer of his own parts. Locke.
A gay seducer of women; a libertine.
The expressed juice of apples. It is used as a beverage, formaking vinegar, and for other purposes.
Of, pertaining to, or designating, a sulphacid of tin (moreexactly called metasulphostannic acid), which is obtained as a darkbrown amorphous substance, H
(Physics) An instrument for ascertaining the specific gravityof bodies.
One who has constant day duties on board ship, and keeps noregular watch. Totten.
